OL,3,CThe apprentice inspiring others with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities to start earning
OL,6,F"Lizzie's better on the till than I
OL,7,Fam," says Vickie Christie, the co-
OL,8,Fowner of a an upmarket refill shop in
OL,9,FPetersfield, Hampshire.
OL,11,F"Lizzie brings her humour - her
OL,12,Fkindness - she's always smiling,"
OL,13,FVickie's business partner, Victoria
OL,14,FPrimrose, adds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
