OL,3,CThe apprentice inspiring others with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities to start earning
OL,6,FVickie and Victoria speak in glowing
OL,7,Fterms about their apprentice, Lizzie
OL,8,FAllen - a young woman, who was born
OL,9,Fwith Down Syndrome, and who is
OL,10,Finspiring others with learning
OL,11,Fdisabilities to start earning and
OL,12,Flearning.
OL,14,FLizzie, 22, is midway through an
OL,15,Fapprenticeship, which was organised
OL,16,Fthrough her local college, at Juniper
OL,17,F- a store where people can do their
OL,18,Fbit for the environment by filling up
OL,19,Fwith reusable jars and containers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775678753
OL,3,CThe apprentice inspiring others with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities to start earning
OL,6,FShe's been hailed by her bosses and
OL,7,Fteachers as an amazing role model, who
OL,8,Fis living proof of just how successful
OL,9,Fan inclusive workplace can be.
OL,11,F"If I am working with Lizzie I have to
OL,12,Fask Lizzie to come and do the till for
OL,13,Fme," Vickie told ITV Meridian.
OL,15,F"I can't do the tills and she's better
OL,16,Fthan me."
OL,18,FVickie and Victoria said having Lizzie
OL,19,Fon board has been hugely positive for
OL,20,Feveryone, helping to tackle
OL,21,Fmisconceptions around Down Syndrome.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
