OL,3,CThe apprentice inspiring others with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities to start earning
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FVickie added: "We don't want to have
OL,12,Fany prejudice against anybody and that
OL,13,Fincludes learning disability
OL,14,Fprejudices, which a lot of people with
OL,15,FDown Syndrome will face.
OL,17,F"And it is a lot of prejudice. There
OL,18,Fare a lot of preconceived ideas and a
OL,19,Flot of surprise that Lizzie is here
OL,20,Fand is as able as she is."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
