OL,3,CThe apprentice inspiring others with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities to start earning
OL,6,FLizzie's qualities and work ethic mean
OL,7,Fshe's become a firm favourite with
OL,8,Fregular customers, including Mary
OL,9,FMazas.
OL,11,F"Right at the beginning she was a bit
OL,12,Fnervous and I've just seen how she's
OL,13,Fimproved and got more confident, so
OL,14,Fher self esteem is up there. We should
OL,15,Fbe doing this more often," Mary said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
