PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775678753
OL,3,CThe apprentice inspiring others with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities to start earning
OL,6,FIt's not just at work where Lizzie is
OL,7,Fexcelling. She's been swimming since
OL,8,Fshe was four-years-old, has won a host
OL,9,Fof international medals and will
OL,10,Fcompete at the World Down Syndrome
OL,11,FSwimming & Artistic Championships
OL,12,Flater this year.
OL,14,FLizzie's mother, Kate Allen, said the
OL,15,Fapprenticeship has allowed Lizzie to
OL,16,Fgrow in confidence "all the time",
OL,17,Fadding: "She's doing incredibly well
OL,18,Fand hopefully this will be the
OL,19,Fspringboard for the future in terms of
OL,20,Femployment for her."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
