CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775678753
OL,3,CThe apprentice inspiring others with
OL,4,Clearning disabilities to start earning
OL,6,FLizzie herself said she is "very
OL,7,Fgrateful" for the experience, saying
OL,8,Fshe believes she's "changed a lot"
OL,9,Fsince starting it.
OL,11,FIt will take Lizzie a total of 18
OL,12,Fmonths to complete her apprenticeship,
OL,13,Fat which point she hopes to hang up
OL,14,Fher apron and move onto her dream job:
OL,15,Fworking in a restaurant.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
